headline: DAT: November truckload volumes lagged robust October
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., December 20, 2024--After gaining momentum throughout the year, last month spot truckload freight volumes retreated to their lowest point since January, said DAT Freight & Analytics, which operates the DAT One freight marketplace and DAT iQ data analytics service.
